---
// Agenda.astro - Seção de Agenda de Shows da banda Plano Marshall
---

<section id="agenda" class="py-20 bg-[#2e2e2e] flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
  <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bebas mb-12 text-[#b9963d] uppercase tracking-wider text-center font-bebas-neue">
      Próximos Shows
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6  ">
      <div class="bg-black p-8 rounded-md text-center border border-[#b9963d]/20">
        <p class="text-[#e0e0e0] mb-6">
          Não perca nenhum show — acompanhe a banda no Instagram e fique por dentro de todas as novidades.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://instagram.com/bandaplanomarshall"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="bg-[#b9963d] hover:bg-[#caa342] text-black font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2 justify-center"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.98-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/>
          </svg>
          ACOMPANHAR NO INSTAGRAM
        </a>
      </div>

  
    </div>

    <!-- Mensagem de Em Breve -->
    <div class="text-center py-16 hidden">
      <div class="bg-black/50 rounded-lg p-8 max-w-md mx-auto border-2 border-dashed border-[#b9963d]/30">
        <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-[#b9963d] mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bebas-neue text-[#b9963d] uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
          Em Breve
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[#e0e0e0] mb-4">
          Estamos preparando shows incríveis para vocês!
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#e0e0e0] text-sm">
          Acompanhem nossas redes sociais para novidades
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
